message: God bless this poor, beautiful family who just tragically lost a wonderful man. Bryan trully was a awesome father,husband and individual that will b missed by so many...i just don't think I'll ever understand the reasoning behind y such horribly things happen to such amazing people! Prayers...rest in peace Bryan!
